---
title: Shrimp and Sun-Dried Tomato Risotto with Garlic Bread
description: Risotto is the stuff that comfort dreams are made of: luxurious, soulful, and satisfying. This version couldn’t be easier and starts as classic as can be, with rich seafood and veggie stocks and the addition of sweet-tart sun-dried tomatoes. It’s finished with plump, piquant, chili-kissed shrimp, and a shower of chives to complement the risotto's creamy richness. Crusty garlic bread is served on the side for scooping up every bit of the dreamy goodness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/shrimp-and-sun-dried-tomato-risotto-411469fb.jpg
